stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Select : Editor öffnet

    Select --> Drawing : Tool R/L/A/B/M
    Select --> Eraser  : Tool E
    Select --> Cropping : Tool C
    Select --> Selecting : Klick auf Shape

    Drawing --> Select : MouseUp + pushUndo (Kind=Shape)
    Eraser --> Select : Klick entfernt + pushUndo (Kind=ShapeRemove)

    Cropping --> CropDragging : MouseDown
    CropDragging --> Cropping : MouseUp
    Cropping --> Select : Apply (pushUndo Crop) / Cancel (Esc)

    Selecting --> SelDragging : MouseDown auf Shape
    SelDragging --> Selecting : MouseUp + pushUndo (Kind=ShapeMove)
    Selecting --> Select : Background-Klick / Esc / Entf (+ ShapeRemove)

    Select --> Saved : Strg+S
    Saved --> [*] : Editor schließt
    Select --> Confirm : Esc / X-Button bei IsDirty
    Confirm --> Select : "Nein" (Cancel)
    Confirm --> [*] : "Ja" (verwerfen)
